    "- 2)Kang, Jun Seok, et al. “Using Text Analysis to Target Government Inspections: Evidence from Restaurant Hygiene Inspections and Online Reviews.” Semantic Scholar, Elseviewer, 13 July 2013, www.semanticscholar.org/paper/Using-Text-Analysis-to-Target-Government-Evidence-Kang-Kuznetsova/9d9e2d6b1c1d2265d6d8e95e8f6f0cc64258fe9f#references.\n",
