    "# Hypothesis\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "I do not believe that reviews can be as thorough as an actual inspector going to and doing an all rounds inspection. This is because reviewers can often be biased or picky about certain aspects of a restaurant which may cause them to write reviews that reflect their subjective feelings rather than an objective perspective.\n*"
   ]
